iwork.eheap2
Class FieldType

java.lang.Object
  iwork.eheap2.FieldType
public class FieldType
extends java.lang.Object

Encodes the type for a field as both an Event Heap standard type string and the equivalent Java class if it exists. Automatically handles converting between the two and using the appropriate representation in comparisons.
